    "excerpt": "A prayer for teachers at the onset of the school year. . . .",
    "content": "\n<table style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" class=\"draggable toggleable-table\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th id=\"x\" style=\"text-align: right;\">Source (Hebrew)</th>\n<th style=\"text-align: left;\"><a href=\"/translate/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Contribute a translation</a></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"he\">\nמִי שֶׁחָנֵן אֶת רַבָּנֵינוּ בּאַהֲבַת הַלִּמּוּד,<br />\nהוּא יְבָרֵךְ אֶתְכֶם בְּסַקְרָנוּת,<br />\nלַהַט הוֹרָאָה וְאַהֲבַת הַסֵּפֶר וְהַחָכְמָה.<br />\n</span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"en\">\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"he\">\nמִי שֶׁחָנֵן אֶת נְבִיאֵי וּנְבִיאוֹת יִשְׂרָאֵל בִּמְסִירוּת הַנֶּפֶשׁ,<br />\nהוּא יִטַּע בָּכֶם אֶת הַכֹּחַ לְהַתְמִיד,<br />\nוִיחַזֵּק אֶת הָאֱמוּנָה שֶׁבַּדֶּרֶךְ.<br />\n</span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"en\">\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"he\">\nמִי שֶּׁבֵּרַךְ אֶת שִׁבְטֵי יִשְׂרָאֵל בְּרוּחַ הַיַּחַד, הָאַחֲוָה, הַשּׁוֹנוּת וְהָאַחְרָיוּת,<br />\nהוּא יַנְחֶה אֶת כֻּלְכֶם בְּרוּחוֹ לְפְעֹל<br />\nלְמַעַן קִיּוּם אֱנוֹשִׁי וְחֶבְרָתִי בְּצַלְמוֹ.<br />\n</span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"en\">\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"he\">\nכְּשֵׁם שֶׁנִּתְבָּרַכְנוּ בָּכֶם הַמּוֹרִים וְהַמּוֹרוֹת,<br />\nכָּךְ תִּתְבָּרְכוּ בְּדַעַת עוֹלָמִים, חֵן וְחֶסֶד וְרַחֲמִים.<br />\nיָאֵר יהוה לִבְּכֶם בֶּאֱמוּנָה,<br />\nוְבְכֹחַ לְהַנְהִיג.<br />\n</span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"en\">\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<hr />\n<p>&#8220;ברכה למורים&#8221; appears on p. 400-401 of <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/תפילת-האדם-סידור-רפורמי-ישראלי-101214578258569\">תפילת האדם, סידור רפורמי ישראלי</a> (2020), the Israeli Reform Movement siddur edited by Rabbi Alona Lisitsa (Ph.D.) and Rabbi Dr. Dalia Marx. This unattributed prayer was shared by Rabbi Lisitsa via the <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/opensiddur/permalink/10157940070937746/\">Open Siddur Project Discussion Group</a> on Facebook.</p>\n<h3>Source(s)</h3>\n<p><span style=\"float: right;\"><div id=\"attachment_32530\" style=\"width: 170px\" class=\"wp-caption alignleft\"><a href=\"https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/tefilat-ha-adam-Israeli-REform-Movement-2020.jpg\" rel=\"lightbox-0\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-32530\" src=\"https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/tefilat-ha-adam-Israeli-REform-Movement-2020-160x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"160\" height=\"300\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-32530\" srcset=\"https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/tefilat-ha-adam-Israeli-REform-Movement-2020-160x300.jpg 160w, https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/tefilat-ha-adam-Israeli-REform-Movement-2020.jpg 505w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 160px) 100vw, 160px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-32530\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Tefilat ha-Adam (Israeli Reform Movement, 2020)</p></div></span>  <span style=\"float: left;\"><div id=\"attachment_33421\" style=\"width: 214px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Tefilat-ha-Adam-p.400-401.jpg\" rel=\"lightbox-1\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-33421\" src=\"https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Tefilat-ha-Adam-p.400-401-204x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"204\" height=\"300\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-33421\" srcset=\"https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Tefilat-ha-Adam-p.400-401-204x300.jpg 204w, https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Tefilat-ha-Adam-p.400-401-698x1024.jpg 698w, https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Tefilat-ha-Adam-p.400-401.jpg 1073w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 204px) 100vw, 204px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-33421\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Tefilat ha-Adam p.400-401</p></div></span><span class=\"\" style=\"display:block;clear:both;height: 0px;border-top-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;\"></span></p>\n",
